A video has emerged on social media of DA Gauteng leader Solly Msimanga after he was allegedly beaten up. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A video has emerged on social media of DA Gauteng leader Solly Msimanga after he was allegedly beaten up. The incident took place on Thursday A person in the video can be heard calling Msimanga a thief and a liar. He claims Msimanga owes him R1.4-million. He further alleges that Msimanga struck him first, leaving him with no choice but to protect himself. Msimanga has denied having any business relations with the man. He's told eNCA that he will open a case of assault.